    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "We're listing this vehicle honestly as a car in mint condition, and we want buyers to have a complete, accurate picture before reaching out. The exterior is truly exceptional \u2014 the paint is deep, glossy, and free of any scratches, chips, or swirl marks. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, and the trim pieces are all intact and pristine. The interior is equally impressive: the upholstery shows no wear, the dashboard and door panels are spotless, and every control, button, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean, all fluids are at proper levels, and there are no leaks or unusual noises. This vehicle drives smoothly and confidently \u2014 steering is responsive, brakes are sharp, and the transmission shifts without hesitation. It has been meticulously maintained, and service records are available for review. If you're looking for a vehicle that feels and performs like new, this is a rare find worth serious consideration.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and the asking price reflects that reality honestly \u2014 please read this entire description before reaching out. The car has significant mechanical and/or cosmetic issues that should be expected at this price point. It may not be reliably drivable without repairs, and buyers should anticipate investing additional money and effort to bring it up to a functional or presentable standard. There are visible signs of wear, damage, or neglect \u2014 whether that's body damage, rust, interior deterioration, or underlying mechanical problems \u2014 and none of that has been hidden or minimized here. This listing is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project vehicle, or a buyer who needs basic transportation and is comfortable with the risks involved. No warranties or guarantees are implied. What you see is what you get, and I've done my best to represent it accurately. If you have questions or want to arrange an inspection before purchase, I strongly encourage that.",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are proud to present one of the finest examples you'll find on the used car market. The exterior is truly exceptional \u2014 the paint finish is deep, glossy, and free of any scratches, chips, dents, or blemishes whatsoever. Panel gaps are tight and uniform, all trim pieces are perfectly intact, and the chrome and brightwork shine as if the car just rolled off the showroom floor. The interior matches the exterior in every way: the upholstery is immaculate with no wear, staining, or fading, all surfaces are pristine, and every switch, button, and control functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is in outstanding health \u2014 the engine runs smoothly and powerfully, all fluids are clean and at proper levels, the transmission shifts crisply, and the brakes, suspension, and steering all feel tight and responsive. There are no warning lights, no known issues, and no deferred maintenance. The tires have substantial tread remaining and are evenly worn. This is a rare opportunity to own a used vehicle that truly feels new \u2014 a car you can drive with complete confidence from day one.",
      "price": 47000.0,
